author: bkrem
message:
fix(engine): ensure requesting client sets own record pre `sendRequest` (#1411)

clientA was setting the history record after it sent a JSON-RPC request
rather than before, so rs-relay seems to process the full request-response
so much faster that clientB had responded before the record had even been
set by A, leading to the "no record in history" error when the response
from clientB came back.
